<Base
  title="Sleeptab — know how much sleep you owe yourself"
  description="Sleeptab turns your Apple Health sleep data into one clear number: your sleep debt."
>
  <h1>Sleeptab</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Know how much sleep you owe yourself. Sleep debt from Apple Health.</p>

  <ul class="features">
    <li><strong>One number that matters</strong>
        <span>Sleeptab reads your sleep from Apple Health and shows your rolling debt over the last 14 nights.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Works with what you have</strong>
        <span>Apple Watch, iPhone, or any sleep tracker that writes to Health. No extra hardware.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Private by design</strong>
        <span>Your health data is read on your device and never leaves it. No account, no ads, no tracking.</span></li>
  </ul>

  <span class="badge">Coming soon to the App Store</span>

  <footer>
    <a href="/sleeptab/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> · <a href="/sleeptab/support/">Support</a>
  </footer>
